{"tid":1953810,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角蚊型地8590萬元批出　低估值下限逾兩成","createTime":"2020-04-01T11:34:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T03:07:22.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"395fc29a4fc8fa1deb7052493632e55d040a1c25","tid":1953810,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T11:34:15.000Z","msg":"地政總署公布，旺角新填地街及上海街住宅地，以8,590萬港元批出，中標財團為鵬程亞洲有限公司。以最大總樓面約24,462方呎計算，每方呎樓面地價約3,512元，較下限估值還低超過兩成。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，上述地皮為接近16年以來，呎價最低的市區住宅地，對上一幅為2004年6月批出的九龍城沙浦道地皮，即御‧豪門現址，當時樓面呎價約2,961元。<br />\n<br />\n上述土地佔地約2,718方呎，是兩年多以來政府推出的最細土地，上周截標反應較市場預期遜色，僅接獲5份標書，投資財團還有信和置業(00083)、寶庭重建發展。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200401/bkn-20200401184424375-0401_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200401%2Fbkn-20200401184424375-0401_00842_001.html&d=fPi9TpucIiEDTgLGk%2FOmnbPGlnsopddeS9pLw%2Bq5tFI%3D&h=c06c32ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200401/bkn-20200401184424375-0401_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"9b83579ca13a33ffd9af61457e935e2e5edf24cf","tid":1953810,"uid":122377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:15:12.000Z","msg":"又話麵粉貴既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6b3f1156d1a25ea1e213fdf2ba6a1cc178c7283","tid":1953810,"uid":41356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:35:04.000Z","msg":"幾億身家嘅有錢佬買塊呢啲地起間獨立屋有無得諗<br />\n雖然旺角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"174b296992cd47699355b620f70abcaacbd1bbe3","tid":1953810,"uid":89869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:39:50.000Z","msg":"旺角上年打到飛起，差唔多日日食山埃彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"327cb56d39d00c09cb1db807c568d71541d47164","tid":1953810,"uid":238920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T02:41:26.00